{"type":"message","id":"4c7f29ae","parentId":"2b646556","timestamp":"2026-04-01T22:35:15.212Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. I've completed the autonomous learning task. Let me provide a brief summary.","thinkingSignature":"6ecb6c07763a702087527db2c838a41f4d89856c5d7309d5b270ad360a74762a"},{"type":"text","text":"**自主学习完成。**\n\n无活跃用户对话，已执行自主学习。整理了3个行业的关键动态并保存至 `memory/学习笔记.md`：\n\n1. **企业数字化转型**：AI原生渗透、低代码普及、ROI优先\n2. **智能安防行业**：AI大模型驱动、预测性安防、四足机器人兴起、合规成红线\n3. **IT运维服务**：AIOps自主运维、可观测性标配、外包行业洗牌、绿色ESG运维\n\n核心交叉洞察：**AI能力是三条业务主线的共同核心竞争力**，道简应聚焦垂直深耕+小切口快落地策略。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4651,"output":147,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48779,"cost":{"input":0.0013953,"output":0.0001764,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0028911299999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775082908602}}
